      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Vitamin C: synthesis cofactor</strong>
        <p>Essential for prolyl hydroxylase and lysyl hydroxylase — the enzymes that cross-link collagen fibers for structural integrity. Without adequate vitamin C, collagen supplementation cannot produce properly formed collagen.</p>
      </div>
